<div class="wp-block-group alignwide portada__rotacion__contenido is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-01814474 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-base-color has-text-color has-link-color has-xx-large-font-size wp-elements-abc2591f56f5c0478c477208c91c4ad9" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700"><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-secondary-color">Ayuda</mark> a un niño enfermo a vivir</h2>



<p class="has-large-font-size">En los slums de Nairobi, miles de niños sufren la pobreza y la falta</p>



<p class="has-large-font-size">de acceso a servicios sanitarios. Con solo 6 €, cubrirás su <strong>asistencia, </strong></p>



<p class="has-large-font-size"><strong>pruebas y tratamiento</strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)">
<div class="wp-block-button is-style-fill"><a class="wp-block-button__link has-large-font-size has-custom-font-size wp-element-button" href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/dona-mukuru/" style="border-radius:60px">Dona</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-cover has-custom-content-position is-position-bottom-center has-base-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-fbc793b5fd6c74e28c47643bd150698a" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)"><img decoding="async" width="1500" height="600" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-4569 size-full" alt="Niños de África favorecidos por nuestra Ong española 100% altruista en África" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ong-espanola-altruista-ninos-africa.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ong-espanola-altruista-ninos-africa.jpg 1500w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ong-espanola-altruista-ninos-africa-800x320.jpg 800w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ong-espanola-altruista-ninos-africa-768x307.jpg 768w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ong-espanola-altruista-ninos-africa-600x240.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-10 has-background-dim"></span><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-cover-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide portada__rotacion__contenido is-vertical is-content-justification-right is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-0949bb80 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-text-align-right has-base-color has-text-color has-link-color has-xx-large-font-size wp-elements-3b59d207fab5b93c75e2fee1018b9de4" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700">Somos de las <mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-secondary-color">únicas</mark> ONG españolas en África <mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-secondary-color">100% altruistas</mark></h2>



<p class="has-text-align-right has-large-font-size">T<strong>u</strong> donación <strong>llega íntegramente</strong> a su destino gracias a que nuestro patronato cubre los gastos de gestión.</p>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-right is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-f1487373 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)">
