</div>
</div>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-cover has-custom-content-position is-position-bottom-center has-base-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-ad9f6fc46056bf277345ff5061e7a5f7" style="padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)"><img decoding="async" width="1500" height="600" class="wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-4570 size-full" alt="Niños de Uganda beneficiados del trabajo de la fundación Pablo por la ayuda a la infancia" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ayuda_infancia-kenia-uganda.jpg" data-object-fit="cover" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ayuda_infancia-kenia-uganda.jpg 1500w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ayuda_infancia-kenia-uganda-800x320.jpg 800w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ayuda_infancia-kenia-uganda-768x307.jpg 768w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ayuda_infancia-kenia-uganda-600x240.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><span aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-20 has-background-dim"></span><div class="wp-block-cover__inner-container has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-cover-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group alignwide portada__rotacion__contenido is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-01814474 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<h1 class="wp-block-heading alignwide has-base-color has-text-color has-link-color has-x-large-font-size wp-elements-173bd535ca9a3a84e1438e367f6fb4d9" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2">Trabajamos por la ayuda a la infancia  <mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-secondary-color"> más vulnerable</mark></h1>



<p class="has-large-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:400">Dignificamos las condiciones de vida de los niños en zonas marginadas de Kenia y Uganda.</p>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)">
