<section class="wp-block-group alignfull portada__lineas has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-e8db78fb wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" id="portada__lineas" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);margin-bottom:12px;padding-right:0;padding-left:0">
<div class="wp-block-group alignfull has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ff778368 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="300" data-aos-duration="500" data-aos-once="true">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center portada__titulo has-primary-color has-text-color has-link-color has-xx-large-font-size wp-elements-961ea0a711cedf3a70fab7b41086af6f" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:700">QUÉ HACEMOS</h2>



<p class="has-text-align-center portada__descripcion has-large-font-size">Como <strong>ONG en África</strong>, centramos nuestros esfuerzos en la supervivencia y el desarrollo de la infancia. Somos una de las <strong>ONGs en África</strong> con gestión 100% altruista, asegurando que cada <strong>donación a la ONG</strong> llegue íntegramente a terreno. Nuestra misión principal es garantizar el derecho a la salud y la alimentación en las zonas más olvidadas</p>
</div>



<div data-slider-type="carousel" data-per-view="3" data-focus-at="1" data-gap="24" data-autoplay="5000" data-hoverpause="true" data-animation-duration="400" data-animation-timing-func="cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.840, 0.440, 1.000)" data-peek-before="24" data-peek-after="24" data-breakpoints="{&quot;600&quot;:{&quot;perView&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;peek&quot;:{&quot;before&quot;:&quot;48&quot;,&quot;after&quot;:&quot;48&quot;},&quot;animationDuration&quot;:&quot;400&quot;},&quot;800&quot;:{&quot;perView&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;peek&quot;:{&quot;before&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;after&quot;:&quot;24&quot;},&quot;animationDuration&quot;:&quot;400&quot;}}" class="wp-block-sci-blocks-sci-slider alignfull sci-blocks-slider glide  portada__lineas__listado" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="300" data-aos-duration="500" data-aos-once="true"><div class="glide__track" data-glide-el="track"><div class="glide__slides is-layout-flow wp-block-sci-blocks-sci-slider-is-layout-flow">
<div class="wp-block-group portada__lineas__listado__bloque has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-style-default"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="756" height="1008" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-ayuda-a-la-infancia.jpg" alt="qué hacemos, ong ayuda a la infancia en África" class="wp-image-2703" style="object-fit:cover" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-ayuda-a-la-infancia.jpg 756w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-ayuda-a-la-infancia-600x800.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 756px) 100vw, 756px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Sanidad</figcaption></figure>



<p class="portada__lineas__listado__bloque__texto has-large-font-size">Ofrecemos asistencia sanitaria de calidad a los niños y mujeres embarazadas.<strong><a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/servicio-de-pediatria-de-lamu/" data-type="page" data-id="46"> <u>Servicio de Pediatría de Lamu</u></a>, <a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/unidad-pediatrica-y-maternal-de-mukuru-nairobi/" data-type="page" data-id="1211"><u>Unidad Pediátrica y Maternal de Mukuru</u></a> y <a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/hospital-materno-infantil-saint-anna-en-webuye-kenia/" data-type="page" data-id="1384"><u>Hospital Materno-Infantil Webuye</u></a></strong>.</p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-group portada__lineas__listado__bloque has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="935" height="1261" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-en-africa-educacion.jpg" alt="Ayuda a la educación ONG en África" class="wp-image-2704" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-en-africa-educacion.jpg 935w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-en-africa-educacion-600x809.jpg 600w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-en-africa-educacion-593x800.jpg 593w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ong-en-africa-educacion-768x1036.jpg 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 935px) 100vw, 935px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Educación</figcaption></figure>



<p class="portada__lineas__listado__bloque__texto has-large-font-size">Ofrecemos oportunidades de un futuro mejor a niños que no estaban escolarizados.<strong><a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/colegio-de-educacion-infantil-y-primaria-en-dokolo/" data-type="page" data-id="841"> <u>Colegio de Dokolo</u></a>,<a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/centros-nutricionales-y-educativos-de-turkana/" data-type="page" data-id="53"> <u>Centros Nutricionales y Educativos de Turkana</u>.</a><br>  </strong></p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-group portada__lineas__listado__bloque has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="924" height="1232" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/formacion-pediatria-kenia.jpg" alt="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" class="wp-image-4508" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/formacion-pediatria-kenia.jpg 924w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/formacion-pediatria-kenia-600x800.jpg 600w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/formacion-pediatria-kenia-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 924px) 100vw, 924px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Formación</figcaption></figure>



<p class="portada__lineas__listado__bloque__texto has-contrast-color has-text-color has-link-color has-large-font-size wp-elements-85dc8938a248d7780ec90dd7b7dc407e">Capacitamos al personal local para que trabaje con autonomía. Conseguimos así que los proyectos sean sostenibles para transferirlos íntegramente a sus comunidades.<a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/cooperacion-internacional-y-voluntariado-en-sede/" data-type="page" data-id="1061"> <strong><u>Cooperantes sanitarios</u></strong> </a>y <a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/cooperacion-internacional-y-voluntariado-en-sede/" data-type="page" data-id="1061"><strong><u>Especialistas para campaña</u></strong>.</a></p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-group portada__lineas__listado__bloque has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="756" height="1008" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/home_alimentacion.jpg" alt="Qué hacemos - Alimentación" class="wp-image-1412" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/home_alimentacion.jpg 756w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/home_alimentacion-600x800.jpg 600w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/home_alimentacion-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 756px) 100vw, 756px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Nutrición</figcaption></figure>



<p class="portada__lineas__listado__bloque__texto has-large-font-size">En los lugares marginales donde trabajamos, es imprescindible garantizar la alimentación a la infancia.<strong><a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/centros-nutricionales-y-educativos-de-turkana/" data-type="page" data-id="53">  <u>Centros Nutricionales de Turkana</u></a>, <a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/colegio-de-educacion-infantil-y-primaria-en-dokolo/" data-type="page" data-id="841"> <u>Colegio de Dokolo</u></a> </strong></p>
</div>
</div></div><div class="glide__arrows" data-glide-el="controls"><button class="glide__arrow glide__arrow--left" data-glide-dir="<"><span class="screen-reader-text">Anterior</span><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 12l10.975 11 2.848-2.828-6.176-6.176H24v-3.992H7.646l6.176-6.176L10.975 1 0 12z"></path></svg></div></button><button class="glide__arrow glide__arrow--right" data-glide-dir="&gt;"><span class="screen-reader-text">Siguiente</span><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="#fff" d="M24 12l-10.975 11-2.848-2.828 6.176-6.176H0v-3.992h16.354l-6.176-6.176L13.025 1 24 12z"></path></svg></div></button></div></div>
</section>



<div id="próximos-eventos" class="wp-block-group bloque-oculto has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center portada__titulo has-primary-color has-text-color has-link-color has-xx-large-font-size wp-elements-f4f4dc46ffdee8ca9baa04ab0517a31f" id="proximos-eventos"><strong>PRÓXIMOS EVENTOS</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-16199c5a wp-block-group-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0">
<div class="wp-block-group evento is-vertical is-content-justification-center is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-d7b04dc7 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-medium evento__imagen" style="margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)"><a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="566" height="800" src="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-566x800.jpg" alt="concierto solidario piano a cuatro manos alcobendas" class="wp-image-4851" title="Fundación Pablo Horstmann" srcset="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-566x800.jpg 566w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-1131x1600.jpg 1131w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-768x1086.jpg 768w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-600x849.jpg 600w, https://www.fundacionpablo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Recital-Piano-Alcobendas-2026-scaled.jpg 1810w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px" /></a></figure>



<div class="wp-block-group evento__informacion is-vertical is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-c9ee0c5a wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<p class="has-medium-font-size"><strong>Concierto Solidario Piano a Cuatro Manos.</strong> Los pianistas Magdalena Ribas y Jorge Gutiérrez Marcet nos ofrecen un especial viaje sonoro del&nbsp;<strong>romanticismo al jazz</strong>, combinado con historias e imágenes, para vivir la música más allá del sonido. A favor de las <a href="https://www.fundacionpablo.org/centros-nutricionales-y-educativos-de-turkana/" data-type="page" data-id="53">Escuelas y Centros Nutricionales de Turkana,</a> Kenia. Precio solidario: <strong>20 €</strong>/persona. Fila cero disponible.</p>



